Jedi Master Yoda's legendary skill means that he rarely faces any true challenges while on missions. But when he receives a mysterious call for help from a distant planet, Yoda must find a way to stop a war without harming any of its combatants - as all of the soldiers are children. The voice talent is provided by members of Casting Call Club (https://castingcall.club).
